
  .- server      client -.
  |    ^            ^    |
  |    |            |    |
  '---------------. |    | 
       |          | |    | 
       '          V '    | 
     READ<--.   WRITE    | 
            |            |
            '------------'


  READ and WRITE are FIFOs

  Server reads from fifo1 and writes to fifo2.
  Client reads from fifo2 and writes to fifo1.


       read-only           write-only
    .------<------:server:------>------.
  fifo1                              fifo2 
    '------>------:client:------<------'
       write-only          read-only
